[https://youtu.be/paoJGMYEEhA](https://youtu.be/paoJGMYEEhA)
# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
$$O(nm)$$
- Space complexity:
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
$$O(nm)\to O(m)$$
# Code
```
class Solution {
public:
    int n, m;
